(29, 19, 1, '2021-03-23 10:16:32', 25, 'comment', '<r><p>目前测试网有3000多种token，以下是官方发行的跨链K资产：<br/>\n<URL url=\"https://okexchain-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/developers/OIP20Tokens/testnet-oip20.html\">https://okexchain-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/developers/OIP20Tokens/testnet-oip20.html</URL></p>\n\n<p>建议所有的项目方使用官方发行的k资产。</p>\n\n<p>关于各币种的精度：<br/>\n（1）测试网-OKT是18位，WOKT是10位<br/>\n（2）主网-WOKT和OKT都会是18位<br/>\n（3）主网K资产的精度设置原则，是与原资产的精度相同的：<br/>\n如OKB原资产是18位，主网的OIP-20也会是18位<br/>\n如果原资产BTC精度是8，BTCK也会是8位</p></r>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '114.247.223.52', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(33, 21, 1, '2021-03-23 22:52:26', 27, 'comment', '<r><p>下载快照<br/>\n快照链接：<URL url=\"https://okexchain-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/resources/snapshot.html\">https://okexchain-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/resources/snapshot.html</URL><br/>\n找到最近一次的测试网快照，下载到本地。<br/>\n例如：<br/>\n$ mv ~/.okexchaind/data ~/.okexchaind/data-bak<br/>\n$ cd ~/.okexchaind <br/>\n$ wget -c <URL url=\"https://ok-public-hk.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/cdn/okexchain/snapshot/okexchain-v0.16.8-testnet-*20210325-height_1588809*.tar.gz\">https://ok-public-hk.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/cdn/okexchain/snapshot/okexchain-v0.16.8-testnet-*20210325-height_1588809*.tar.gz</URL> # 该链接会定期更新，请使用最新链接<br/>\n$ tar -zxvf okexchain-v0.16.8-testnet-*.tar.gz</p>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>1，使用docker方式启动</H2>\n<p>下载docker镜像<br/>\ndocker pull okexchain/fullnode-testnet:latest</p>\n\n<p>运行镜像<br/>\ndocker run -d --name okexchain-testnet-fullnode -v ~/.okexchaind/data:/root/.okexchaind/data/ -p 8545:8545 okexchain/fullnode-testnet:latest</p>\n\n<p>查看日志<br/>\ndocker logs --tail 100 -f okexchain-testnet-fullnode</p>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>2，使用okexchaind方式启动</H2>\n<p>编译okexchaind，使用代码版本：<URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/okexchain/releases\">https://github.com/okx/okexchain/releases</URL><br/>\n$ make testnet</p>\n\n<p>初始化节点配置 (如果已经初始化，可以跳过该步骤)<br/>\n$ okexchaind init your_custom_moniker --chain-id okexchain-65 --home ~/.okexchaind</p>\n\n<p>启动全节点<br/>\n$ export OKEXCHAIN_SEEDS=\"b7c6bdfe0c3a6c1c68d6d6849f1b60f566e189dd@3.13.150.20:36656,d7eec05e6449945c8e0fd080d58977d671eae588@35.176.111.229:36656,223b5b41d1dba9057401def49b456630e1ab2599@18.162.106.25:36656\"<br/>\n$ okexchaind start --chain-id okexchain-65 --home ~/.okexchaind --p2p.seeds $OKEXCHAIN_SEEDS</p>\n\n</r>', '2021-08-24 07:22:46', 27, '2021-08-24 07:24:29', 27, '103.35.74.167', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(34, 22, 1, '2021-03-23 22:53:04', 27, 'comment', '<t><p>因为 OKT 不是 OIP20 标准的代币, 所以在智能合约中实现币币兑换的时候, 我们需要将 OKT 封装成 OIP20 标准代币, 而 WOKT 就是将 OKT 封装成 OIP20 标准的代币，按照 1 OKT = 1 WOKT，方便OKT直接与其他代币交易。</p></t>', '2021-04-03 09:44:16', 28, NULL, NULL, '103.35.74.167', 0, 1, 0, 0),
