(61, 38, 1, '2021-03-29 02:23:37', 28, 'comment', '<r><H2><s>## </s>节点运行过程中报open  too many files错误</H2>\n<p>如图所示：<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-05/1628128156-103841-132424ff-1e3a-43ab-8ce7-b400780ecd5c.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-05/1628128156-103841-132424ff-1e3a-43ab-8ce7-b400780ecd5c.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>原因</H2>\n<p>数据库服务器或是应用程序在某些时候有可能会由于打开了过多的文件（ too many open files）而导致报错。大多数情况下，这是由于配置参数过小，不能满足应用的需求。</p>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>解决办法</H2>\n<H3><s>###  </s>1. 编辑limits.conf</H3>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>$ sudo su\n$ vi /etc/security/limits.conf<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>将以下内容放到文件中</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>root soft nofile 1000000\nroot hard nofile 1000000\n\\* soft nofile 1000000\n\\* hard nofile 1000000<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n\n<H3><s>###  </s>2. 设置sysctl.conf<e> </e></H3>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>$ mv /etc/sysctl.conf /etc/sysctl.conf.bak\n$ vi /etc/sysctl.conf <i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<p>以下内容放入/etc/sysctl.conf</p> \n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>net.ipv6.conf.all.disable_ipv6 = 1\nnet.ipv6.conf.default.disable_ipv6 = 1\nnet.ipv6.conf.lo.disable_ipv6 = 1\n \nvm.swappiness = 0\nnet.ipv4.neigh.default.gc_stale_time=120\nnet.ipv4.conf.all.rp_filter=0\nnet.ipv4.conf.default.rp_filter=0\nnet.ipv4.conf.default.arp_announce = 2\nnet.ipv4.conf.lo.arp_announce=2\nnet.ipv4.conf.all.arp_announce=2\nnet.ipv4.tcp_max_tw_buckets = 5000\nnet.ipv4.tcp_syncookies = 1\nnet.ipv4.tcp_max_syn_backlog = 1024\nnet.ipv4.tcp_synack_retries = 2\n \nnet.core.wmem_default = 8388608\nnet.core.rmem_default = 8388608\n \nnet.core.wmem_max = 16777216\nnet.ipv4.tcp_rmem = 4096 87380 16777216\nnet.ipv4.tcp_wmem = 4096 65536 16777216\nnet.ipv4.tcp_timestamps = 0\nnet.ipv4.tcp_window_scaling = 1\nnet.ipv4.tcp_sack = 1\nnet.ipv4.tcp_no_metrics_save = 1\n \nnet.core.netdev_max_backlog = 262144\nnet.ipv4.tcp_max_syn_backlog = 262144\nnet.ipv4.tcp_max_tw_buckets = 60000\nnet.ipv4.ip_local_port_range = 1024 65000\n \nnet.ipv4.tcp_fin_timeout = 5\nnet.ipv4.tcp_tw_recycle = 1\nnet.ipv4.tcp_retries1 = 2\nnet.ipv4.tcp_retries2 = 10\nnet.ipv4.tcp_synack_retries = 2\nnet.ipv4.tcp_syn_retries = 2\nnet.ipv4.tcp_syncookies = 1\nnet.ipv4.tcp_tw_reuse = 1\n  \nnet.ipv4.tcp_max_orphans = 3276800\nnet.ipv4.tcp_mem = 94500000 915000000 927000000\nnet.ipv4.tcp_keepalive_time = 10\nfs.file-max = 1000000\n \nnet.core.somaxconn = 65535\n \nkernel.kptr_restrict=1<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<p>再执行</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>$ sysctl -p  # 运行生效\n$ systemctl restart docker<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n\n<H3><s>###  </s>3. 查看结果</H3>\n<p>$ ulimit -a # 再次进入查看</p></r>', '2021-08-21 00:16:58', 27, NULL, NULL, '43.245.196.166', 0, 1, 0, 0),
