(110, 60, 1, '2021-04-15 09:13:32', 24, 'comment', '<r><p>OKExChain saw significant progress and functional enhancements last month.</p>\n\n<p>One of the main achievements for the blockchain protocol was the integration of Chainlink price oracles. OKExChain also launched its first , where community members can interact in both English and Chinese.</p> \n\n<p>The OKExChain testnet also launched functional upgrades — such as increased queries per second and block production efficiency in the Ethereum Virtual Machine module — and added new connections in Ethereum WebSocket.</p>\n\n<p>In terms of ecosystem development, OKExChain secured 11 media partners and welcomed a new security partnership with Armors.</p>\n\n<p>For full details on OKExChain\'s monthly development, please refer to our new one-pager below:</p>\n\n<UPL-FILE content=\"okexchain-monthly-report-mar.pdf\" size=\"105kB\" uuid=\"b90ab4d4-e29b-4637-b2f1-fb159f506ee8\"><s>[upl-file uuid=b90ab4d4-e29b-4637-b2f1-fb159f506ee8 size=105kB]</s>okexchain-monthly-report-mar.pdf<e>[/upl-file]</e></UPL-FILE>\n\n</r>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '210.0.158.203', 0, 1, 0, 0),
