(127, 70, 1, '2021-04-25 06:07:10', 31, 'comment', '<r><H1><s># </s>OKC主网v0.18.1升级步骤</H1>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>开始</H2>\n\n<p>搭建最新主网前，可了解<URL url=\"https://okc-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/getting-start/join-okexchain-mainnet.html\"><s>[</s>文档<e>](https://okc-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/getting-start/join-okexchain-mainnet.html)</e></URL>。</p>\n\n\n<H2><s>## </s>基于v0.16.3版本升级主网</H2>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>1. 停止节点，并指定 \'halt-height = 2322600\' 重新启动节点</H3>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>export EXCHAIND_PATH=~/.exchaind (如果你原有的节点目录不是 ~/.exchaind, 那么就指定你自己的节点目录)\nokexchaind start --chain-id okexchain-66 --halt-height 2322600 --home ${EXCHAIND_PATH}<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>等全网节点高度达到2322600后，进行以下操作：</H3>\n<H3><s>### </s>2.可通过以下两种方式获取 genesis.json 文件</H3>\n\n<H4><s>#### </s>2.1 通过 exchaind 导出</H4>\n\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>   cd ${EXCHAIND_PATH}\n   git clone -b v0.16.3.1 https://github.com/okx/exchain.git\n   cd exchain\n   make install\n   okexchaind export --home ${EXCHAIND_PATH} --height=2322600 --for-zero-height --log_level evm:debug --log_file ./export.log --log_stdout=false &gt; ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis_no_migrate.json\n   git checkout v0.18.1\n   make GenesisHeight=2322600 install  # v0.19.0之后使用 make mainnet\n   exchaind migrate v0.18 ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis_no_migrate.json --chain-id=exchain66 &gt; ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis.json\n   mv ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/okexchaind.toml ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/exchaind.toml<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<H4><s>#### </s>2.2 从官方下载 genesis.json</H4>\n\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>   wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okx/mainnet/main/genesis.json -O ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis.json<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<p>注意：不管用哪种方式获取genesis.json文件，都应该检查下genesis.json文件的shasum值</p>\n\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>$ shasum -a 256 ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis.json\n0958b6c9f5f125d1d6b8f56e042fa8a71b1880310227b8b2f27ba93ff7cd673b  ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis.json<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>3. 编译</H3>\n\n<p>在 <URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/tag/v0.18.1\"><s>[</s>version v0.18.1<e>](https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/tag/v0.18.1)</e></URL> 版本上编译exchaind</p>\n\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>   cd ${EXCHAIND_PATH}\n   git clone -b v0.18.1 https://github.com/okx/exchain.git\n   cd exchain\n   make GenesisHeight=2322600 install  # v0.19.0之后使用 make mainnet<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>4. 重置数据</H3>\n\n<p><C><s>`</s>exchaind unsafe-reset-all --home ${EXCHAIND_PATH}<e>`</e></C></p>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>5. 启动</H3>\n\n<p><C><s>`</s>exchaind start --chain-id exchain-66 --home ${EXCHAIND_PATH}<e>`</e></C></p>\n\n\n<H2><s>## </s>搭建新节点</H2>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>1. 在 <URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/tag/v0.18.1\"><s>[</s>version v0.18.1<e>](https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/tag/v0.18.1)</e></URL> 版本上编译exchaind</H3>\n\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>export EXCHAIND_PATH=~/.exchaind (你也可以指定其他目录)<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>2. 启动</H3>\n\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>exchaind init your_custom_moniker --chain-id exchain-66 --home ${EXCHAIND_PATH}\n\nwget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okx/mainnet/main/genesis.json -O ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis.json\n\nexport EXCHAIN_SEEDS=\"e926c8154a2af4390de02303f0977802f15eafe2@3.16.103.80:26656,7fa5b1d1f1e48659fa750b6aec702418a0e75f13@35.177.8.240:26656,c8f32b793871b56a11d94336d9ce6472f893524b@18.167.16.85:26656\"\n\nexchaind start --chain-id exchain-66 --home ${EXCHAIND_PATH} --p2p.seeds $EXCHAIN_SEEDS<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<p>注意：检查genesis.json文件的shasum值</p>\n\n<CODE lang=\"bash\"><s>```bash</s><i>\n</i>$ shasum -a 256 ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis.json\n0958b6c9f5f125d1d6b8f56e042fa8a71b1880310227b8b2f27ba93ff7cd673b  ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis.json<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE></r>', '2022-03-23 09:53:30', 1, NULL, NULL, '43.245.222.183', 0, 1, 0, 0),
