(131, 71, 1, '2021-04-25 08:22:08', 31, 'comment', '<r><H1><s># </s>OKC主网v0.18.1节点搭建</H1>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>一、使用二进制文件搭建新节点</H2>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>1. 用 <URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/tag/v0.18.1\"><s>[</s>version v0.18.1<e>](https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/tag/v0.18.1)</e></URL> 版本上编译exchaind</H3>\n\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>export EXCHAIND_PATH=~/.exchaind (你也可以指定其他目录)\ncd ${EXCHAIND_PATH}\ngit clone -b v0.18.1 https://github.com/okx/exchain.git\ncd exchain\nmake GenesisHeight=2322600 install  # v0.19.0之后使用 make mainnet<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>2. 启动</H3>\n\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>exchaind init your_custom_moniker --chain-id exchain-66 --home ${EXCHAIND_PATH}\n\nwget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okx/mainnet/main/genesis.json -O ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis.json\n\nexport EXCHAIN_SEEDS=\"e926c8154a2af4390de02303f0977802f15eafe2@3.16.103.80:26656,7fa5b1d1f1e48659fa750b6aec702418a0e75f13@35.177.8.240:26656,c8f32b793871b56a11d94336d9ce6472f893524b@18.167.16.85:26656\"\n\nexchaind start --chain-id exchain-66 --home ${EXCHAIND_PATH} --p2p.seeds $EXCHAIN_SEEDS<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<p>注意：检查genesis.json文件的shasum值</p>\n\n<CODE lang=\"bash\"><s>```bash</s><i>\n</i>$ shasum -a 256 ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis.json\n0958b6c9f5f125d1d6b8f56e042fa8a71b1880310227b8b2f27ba93ff7cd673b  ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis.json<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>二、使用docker运行全节点</H2>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>1. 创建数据文件夹</H3>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>mkdir -p ~/.exchaind/data\necho \'{\\n\"height\": \"0\",\\n\"round\": \"0\",\\n\"step\": 0\\n}\' &gt; ~/.exchaind/data/priv_validator_state.json<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<H3><s>### </s>2. 启动docker</H3>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>docker run -d --name exchain-mainnet-fullnode -v ~/.exchaind/data:/root/.exchaind/data/ -p 8545:8545 -p 26656:26656 okexchain/fullnode-mainnet:latest<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<H3><s>### </s>3. 查看docker运行日志</H3>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>docker logs --tail 100 -f exchain-mainnet-fullnode<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<H3><s>### </s>4. 停止docker容器</H3>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>docker rm -f exchain-mainnet-fullnode<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<H3><s>### </s>5. 重新启动</H3>\n<p>第二次启动的时候，不需要再次创建数据文件夹，可以使用之前的数据文件夹，在之前的数据基础上继续运行。</p>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>docker run -d --name exchain-mainnet-fullnode -v ~/.exchaind/data:/root/.exchaind/data/ -p 8545:8545 -p 26656:26656 okexchain/fullnode-mainnet:latest<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n</r>', '2022-03-23 09:53:05', 1, NULL, NULL, '43.245.222.183', 0, 1, 0, 0),
