(144, 79, 1, '2021-05-10 05:53:30', 25, 'comment', '<r><p>OKExchain(简称OEC)支持双地址格式，一把私钥对应两种格式的地址：ex前缀地址与0x前缀地址，两种格式地址对应同一份资产。OKEx已支持0x地址格式的充值，若用户使用仅支持ex地址格式的钱包，可以按照如下过程进行充值：</p>\n\n<p>第一步，进入OKEx OKT充币界面，复制充币地址</p>\n<UPL-IMAGE content=\"555.png\" size=\"11kB\" url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-05-10/1620625879-568199-555.png\" uuid=\"54a9cd7f-5299-4501-ac36-3cdb480b8672\"><s>[upl-image uuid=54a9cd7f-5299-4501-ac36-3cdb480b8672 size=11kB url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-05-10/1620625879-568199-555.png]</s>555.png<e>[/upl-image]</e></UPL-IMAGE>\n\n<p>第二步，打开OKlink，找到OKExchain浏览器，查询上面的充币地址，找到对应的ex格式地址</p>\n<UPL-IMAGE content=\"6666.png\" size=\"10kB\" url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-05-10/1620625896-396527-6666.png\" uuid=\"0c2d1671-8296-4151-a8b5-1a517f4e93c4\"><s>[upl-image uuid=0c2d1671-8296-4151-a8b5-1a517f4e93c4 size=10kB url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-05-10/1620625896-396527-6666.png]</s>6666.png<e>[/upl-image]</e></UPL-IMAGE>\n\n<p>第三步，打开OKT钱包的发送界面，将OKT发送至对应的ex格式地址</p>\n<UPL-IMAGE content=\"c06a94ef8d0d68d4050f5328f276857.jpg\" size=\"88kB\" url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-05-10/1620625924-666818-c06a94ef8d0d68d4050f5328f276857.jpg\" uuid=\"b5e75f5e-282d-44b9-8718-93ebd7b14552\"><s>[upl-image uuid=b5e75f5e-282d-44b9-8718-93ebd7b14552 size=88kB url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-05-10/1620625924-666818-c06a94ef8d0d68d4050f5328f276857.jpg]</s>c06a94ef8d0d68d4050f5328f276857.jpg<e>[/upl-image]</e></UPL-IMAGE>\n\n<p>等待确认，充值成功<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-05-10/1620628256-707137-77777-1.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-05-10/1620628256-707137-77777-1.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n</r>', '2021-05-10 06:31:00', 1, NULL, NULL, '139.162.123.188', 0, 1, 0, 0),
