(150, 85, 1, '2021-05-13 03:13:34', 30, 'comment', '<t><p>主网节点调整gas price为0.1gwei，方法如下：<br/>\n修改节点配置文件 ~/.exchaind/data/config/exchaind.toml，把里面minimum-gas-prices的值修改为0.0000000001okt，修改后重启节点。</p>\n</t>', '2021-05-13 05:00:04', 30, NULL, NULL, '103.113.156.47', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(151, 87, 1, '2021-05-13 03:19:37', 30, 'comment', '<r><p>一、主网节点升级到v0.18.3.1，方法：<br/>\n1、如果节点是以编译二进制的方式启动的，拉取最新代码 <URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/tag/v0.18.3.1\">https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/tag/v0.18.3.1</URL> 重新编译二进制，命令如下：</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>export EXCHAIND_PATH=~/.okexchaind  #(如果您的--home目录不是~/.okexchaind，请指定您自己的--home目录)\ncd ${EXCHAIND_PATH}\nrm -rf exchain\ngit clone -b v0.18.3.1 https://github.com/okx/exchain.git\ncd exchain\nmake GenesisHeight=2322600 install  # v0.19.0之后使用 make mainnet<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>然后重启节点，命令如下：</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>export EXCHAIN_SEEDS=\"e926c8154a2af4390de02303f0977802f15eafe2@3.16.103.80:26656,7fa5b1d1f1e48659fa750b6aec702418a0e75f13@35.177.8.240:26656,c8f32b793871b56a11d94336d9ce6472f893524b@18.167.16.85:26656\"\n\nexchaind start --chain-id exchain-66 --home ${EXCHAIND_PATH} --p2p.seeds $EXCHAIN_SEEDS<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>2、如果是使用官方镜像方式启动的节点，docker pull最新镜像，命令如下：</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>docker pull okexchain/fullnode-mainnet:latest<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>然后重启节点，命令如下：</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>docker rm -f exchain-mainnet-fullnode\ndocker run -d --name exchain-mainnet-fullnode -v ~/.exchaind/data:/root/.exchaind/data/ -p 8545:8545 -p 26656:26656 okexchain/fullnode-mainnet:latest<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<p>二、主网节点调整gas price为0.1gwei，方法如下：<br/>\n修改节点配置文件 ~/.exchaind/data/config/exchaind.toml，把里面minimum-gas-prices的值修改为0.0000000001okt，修改后重启节点。</p>\n</r>', '2021-08-24 07:20:26', 28, '2021-09-16 10:20:02', 30, '103.113.156.47', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(152, 88, 1, '2021-05-13 03:27:45', 38, 'comment', '<r><p>在使用最新版本(v9.5.0/v9.5.1)MetaMask执行exchain主网或测试网操作时，会失败报错：<C><s>`</s>This method only supports 0x-prefixed  hex strings but input was: OKT<e>`</e></C><br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-05-13/1620876082-770339-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-05-13/1620876082-770339-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n<p><STRONG><s>**</s>错误原因<e>**</e></STRONG>：MetaMask v9.5.0/v9.5.1两个版本中有bug<br/>\n<STRONG><s>**</s>两种解决方法<e>**</e></STRONG>：<br/>\n<STRONG><s>**</s><EM><s>*</s>注意：务必先备份私钥、助记词等账户、网络信息，并将MetaMask移除。<e>*</e></EM><e>**</e></STRONG></p>\n<LIST type=\"decimal\"><LI><s>1. </s>升级MetaMask到v9.5.2<br/>\n    由于当前MetaMaskp<URL url=\"https://metamask.io/download.html\"><s>[</s>官网安装页面<e>](https://metamask.io/download.html)</e></URL>提供的安装版本是v9.5.1，升级v9.5.2需要从<URL url=\"https://github.com/MetaMask/metamask-extension/releases\"><s>[</s>这里<e>](https://github.com/MetaMask/metamask-extension/releases)</e></URL>下载插件手动安装。</LI>\n<LI><s>2. </s>降级MetaMask到v9.4.0<br/>\n    降级MetaMask到v9.4.0需要从<URL url=\"https://github.com/MetaMask/metamask-extension/releases\"><s>[</s>这里<e>](https://github.com/MetaMask/metamask-extension/releases)</e></URL>下载插件手动安装。</LI></LIST></r>', '2021-05-13 03:39:23', 38, NULL, NULL, '43.245.222.33', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(153, 89, 1, '2021-05-17 09:33:09', 34, 'comment', '<r><H2><s>## </s>主网节点升级到最新版本方法：</H2>\n<H3><s>### </s>1. 如果节点是以编译二进制的方式启动，命令如下：</H3>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>export EXCHAIND_PATH=~/.okexchaind  #(如果您的--home目录不是~/.okexchaind，请指定您自己的--home目录)\ncd ${EXCHAIND_PATH}\nrm -rf exchain\ngit clone -b latest_version https://github.com/okx/exchain.git  # latest_version可以通过链接 https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/latest 查看\ncd exchain\nmake mainnet <i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p><COLOR color=\"red\"><s>[color=red]</s>注1：务必用 <STRONG><s>**</s>make mainnet<e>**</e></STRONG> 编译<br/>\n注2：latest_version可以通过链接 <URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/latest\">https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/latest</URL> 查看<br/>\n<e>[/color]</e></COLOR><br/>\n然后重启节点，命令如下：</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>export EXCHAIN_SEEDS=\"e926c8154a2af4390de02303f0977802f15eafe2@3.16.103.80:26656,7fa5b1d1f1e48659fa750b6aec702418a0e75f13@175.41.191.69:26656,c8f32b793871b56a11d94336d9ce6472f893524b@35.74.8.189:26656\"\n\n# 务必先stop掉(建议使用 kill -2 pid 方式)正在运行的exchaind进程，再使用新编译的exchaind启动\nexchaind start --chain-id exchain-66 --home ${EXCHAIND_PATH} --p2p.seeds $EXCHAIN_SEEDS --mempool.sort_tx_by_gp<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<H3><s>### </s>2. 如果是使用官方镜像方式启动的节点，docker pull最新镜像，命令如下：</H3>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>docker pull okexchain/fullnode-mainnet:latest<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>然后重启节点，命令如下：</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>docker rm -f exchain-mainnet-fullnode\ndocker run -d --name exchain-mainnet-fullnode -v ~/.exchaind/data:/root/.exchaind/data/ -p 8545:8545 -p 26656:26656 okexchain/fullnode-mainnet:latest<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n</r>', '2021-09-16 10:22:40', 30, NULL, NULL, '111.200.241.55', 0, 1, 0, 0),
