IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-07-05/1625468762-954489-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-07-05/1625468762-954489-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p></LI></LIST>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>关于OKExChain</H3>\n<p>OKExChain主页：<URL url=\"https://www.ouyi.cc/okexchain\">https://www.ouyi.cc/okexchain</URL><br/>\nOKExChain文档：<URL url=\"https://okexchain-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest\">https://okexchain-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest</URL><br/>\nOKExChain论坛：<URL url=\"https://forum.okt.club/\">https://forum.okt.club/</URL><br/>\nGitHub: <URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/okexchain\">https://github.com/okx/okexchain</URL><br/>\nTelegram中文：<URL url=\"https://t.me/okexchain_cn\">https://t.me/okexchain_cn</URL><br/>\nTelegram英文：<URL url=\"https://t.me/okexchainglobal\">https://t.me/okexchainglobal</URL><br/>\nTelegram开发者：<URL url=\"https://t.me/okexchaintech\">https://t.me/okexchaintech</URL></p>\n\n\n\n</r>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '13.75.106.76', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(213, 116, 1, '2021-07-12 09:25:34', 23, 'comment', '<r><H3><s>### </s>OKExChain每周数据</H3>\n<p>● 总交易笔数：1,601,701 (+222,354) <br/>\n● 节点数：54<br/>\n● OKT流通量：12,479,885.5 (+82,238)<br/>\n● OKT流通率：29.74% (+0.2%)<br/>\n● 累计提案数：31 (+1)<br/>\n● 代币数量：422 (+14) <br/>\n● 持币地址数：201,110 (+87,996) <br/>\n● 合约总数：706 (+29)<br/>\n● 去重后合约数量：336  (+19)</p>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>OKExChain抵押借贷总量：</H3>\n<p><UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-07-12/1626081092-963038-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-07-12/1626081092-963038-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n<H3><s>### </s>OKExChain锁仓市值：</H3>\n<p><UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-07-12/1626081196-952168-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-07-12/1626081196-952168-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n<H3><s>### </s>OKExChain生态发展</H3>\n<p>OKExChain上目前已运行共20款Dapp，本周新增2款，总TVL达$1.26亿<br/>\n本周新增：Lending Protocol ：DeFiner和Tool：Bulksender</p>\n<H3><s>### </s>OKExChain生态与基础设施进展</H3>\n<LIST type=\"decimal\"><LI><s>1. </s>OKExChain于上周发布6月技术与生态月报，总计了OKExChain在6月份的技术进展和生态拓展近况：<br/>\n<URL url=\"https://www.ouyi.cc/academy/zh/okexchain-monthly-report-june-2021\">https://www.ouyi.cc/academy/zh/okexchain-monthly-report-june-2021</URL></LI>\n<LI><s>2. </s>7月11日OKExChain Grant Hackathon落幕，参赛团队通过HackerLink提交项目申请，共获得32875.7 OKT（价值超180万美元）资助，其中757.6 OKT由OKExChain官方资助，32118.07 OKT来自社区捐赠。请关注我们获得最新获奖项目进展。<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-07-12/1626081609-215711-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-07-12/1626081609-215711-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></LI>\n<LI><s>3. </s>DeFiner于2021年7月7日 00:00 (UTC) 上线OKExChain并开启FIN Shark Pool挖矿活动，质押 USDT、OKB、OKT、BTCK、ETHK 以及 FIN 获取挖矿收益。DeFiner项目创始人 Jason还于上周在OKExChain社群进行了AMA分享。</LI>\n<LI><s>4. </s>由于OKExChain已经支持EVM和智能合约，欧易OKEx于2021年7月9日17:00 (HKT) 永久下线OKEx Swap和OKEx Farm产品。这两款产品都是基于OKExChain系统合约开发的，目前OKExChain已经支持EVM和智能合约，系统合约产品因此完成了他的历史使命。未来用户将体验到的是丰富多彩的基于EVM开发的智能合约产品。</LI>\n<LI><s>5. </s>OKExChain于上周更新了最新的OEC生态版图https://twitter.com/OKExChain/status/1413096352028839938?s=20，目前共有涉及钱包、跨链桥以及看板等多领域的超过35个项目已加入OKExChain生态，OEC生态在稳步拓展中，期待未来会有更多更优质的项目加入OKExChain主网，共同建设OEC生态。</LI></LIST>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>关于OKExChain</H3>\n<p>OKExChain主页：<URL url=\"https://www.ouyi.cc/okexchain\">https://www.ouyi.cc/okexchain</URL><br/>\nOKExChain文档：<URL url=\"https://okexchain-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest\">https://okexchain-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest</URL><br/>\nOKExChain论坛：<URL url=\"https://forum.okt.club/\">https://forum.okt.club/</URL><br/>\nGitHub: <URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/okexchain\">https://github.com/okx/okexchain</URL><br/>\nTelegram中文：<URL url=\"https://t.me/okexchain_cn\">https://t.me/okexchain_cn</URL><br/>\nTelegram英文：<URL url=\"https://t.me/okexchainglobal\">https://t.me/okexchainglobal</URL><br/>\nTelegram开发者：<URL url=\"https://t.me/okexchaintech\">https://t.me/okexchaintech</URL></p>\n\n\n\n\n</r>', '2021-07-12 09:47:30', 23, NULL, NULL, '13.94.38.186', 0, 1, 0, 0),
