(242, 128, 1, '2021-07-30 07:55:13', 28, 'comment', '<r><p>归档节点跟全节点的搭建过程一致。可参考：<URL url=\"https://forum.okt.club/d/127-faq\">https://forum.okt.club/d/127-faq</URL><br/>\n区别仅仅是配置参数不同。</p>\n\n<p>配置参数：</p>\n\n<p>—pruning=nothing</p>\n\n<p>完整的参数配置：<br/>\n一、exchaind方式启动</p>\n\n<p>--chain-id exchain-66 <br/>\n--home /root/.exchaind <br/>\n--p2p.seeds e926c8154a2af4390de02303f0977802f15eafe2@3.16.103.80:26656,7fa5b1d1f1e48659fa750b6aec702418a0e75f13@35.177.8.240:26656,c8f32b793871b56a11d94336d9ce6472f893524b@18.167.16.85:26656<br/>\n--mempool.sort_tx_by_gp <br/>\n--pruning=nothing <br/>\n--mempool.size 10000 <br/>\n--mempool.recheck 0 <br/>\n--mempool.force_recheck_gap 2000 <br/>\n--max-open 20000 <br/>\n--close-mutex 1 <br/>\n--pruning=nothing <br/>\n--enable-bloom-filter 1</p>\n\n\n\n<p>二、docker方式启动</p>\n    <br/>\n<LIST><LI><s>- </s>OKEXCHAIN_BACKUP=0</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>OKEXCHAIN_MEMPOOL_SORT_TX_BY_GP=true</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>OKEXCHAIN_MEMPOOL_SIZE=10000</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>OKEXCHAIN_MEMPOOL_RECHECK=0</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>OKEXCHAIN_MEMPOOL_FORCE_RECHECK_GAP=2000</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>OKEXCHAIN_MAX_OPEN=20000</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>OKEXCHAIN_CLOSE_MUTEX=1</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>OKEXCHAIN_PRUNING=nothing</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>OKEXCHAIN_TX_INDEX_INDEXER=kv</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>OKEXCHAIN_ENABLE_BLOOM_FILTER=1</LI></LIST></r>', '2021-07-30 10:30:20', 28, NULL, NULL, '103.35.74.167', 0, 1, 0, 0),
