(250, 134, 1, '2021-08-02 10:16:07', 23, 'comment', '<r><H3><s>### </s>1. OKExChain每周数据</H3>\n\n<LIST><LI><s>- </s>总交易笔数：5,524,960 (+3,854,766)    </LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>节点数：54</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>OKT流通量：12,720,324 (+77,927)</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>OKT流通率：30.31% (+0.18%)</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>累计提案数：36 (+4)</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>代币数量：3,364 (+2,920) </LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>持币地址数：269,775 (+67,574) </LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>合约总数：5,387 (+4,665)</LI>\n<LI><s>- </s>去重后合约数量：2868 (+2,528)</LI>  </LIST>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>2. OKExChain抵押借贷总量：</H3>\n<p><UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-02/1627899184-32830-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-02/1627899184-32830-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>3. OKExChain锁仓市值：</H3>\n<p><UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-02/1627899212-74930-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-02/1627899212-74930-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>4. OKExChain生态发展</H3>\n<p>OKExChain上目前已运行共25款Dapp，上周新增2款，总TVL达$16亿；</p>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>5. OKExChain生态与基础设施进展</H3>\n\n<p>OKExChain于7月28日正式开启主网启动的第三阶段。 在第三阶段，OEC对所有开发者开放，任何人都可以在链上自由部署项目。在第三阶段开启短短24小时内，OKExChain链上TVL就已经突破10亿美金，可以显示出社区和用户对于OEC的未来生态发展的支持与肯定。<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-02/1627899268-47629-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-02/1627899268-47629-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n <p>根据OKLink数据显示，OKExChain目前总TVL已达16亿，目前锁仓排行前三的项目分别是CherrySwap，KSwap和Flux。<br/>\n <UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-02/1627899304-789740-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-02/1627899304-789740-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>OEC风险提示:</H3>\n<p>OEC是开放的去中心化公链，任何人都可自由部署项目，参与和使用链上应用以及交易加密货币都存在巨大风险，请您谨慎参与。</p>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>关于OKExChain</H3>\n<p>OKExChain主页：<URL url=\"https://www.o