(253, 136, 1, '2021-08-02 10:27:41', 28, 'comment', '<r><TABLE><THEAD><TR><i>| </i><TH>序号</TH><i> | </i><TH>不兼容项</TH><i>                                                  | </i><TH>OKC</TH><i>                                                    | </i><TH>Ethereum</TH><i>                                                     | </i><TH>导致的问题</TH><i>                                      | </i><TH>解决方案</TH><i>                                                     |</i></TR></THEAD><i>\n| ---- | --------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |</i>\n<TBODY><TR><i>| </i><TD>1</TD><i>    | </i><TD>txhash生成算法</TD><i>                                            | </i><TD>okexchain团队基于官方的etherjs上实现了amino+sha256算法，可以生成exchain或cosmos风格的交易hash。</TD><i> | </i><TD>可链下计算。 txhash计算方式是 <C><s>`</s>keccak256(signedTransaction）<e>`</e></C>。</TD><i> | </i><TD>使用ether.js或者hardhat在OEC部署合约时 会报错。</TD><i> | </i><TD>使用okexchain团队提供的工具，<URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/ethers.js/tree/ray\"><s>[</s>项目地址<e>](https://github.com/okx/ethers.js/tree/ray)</e></URL>。</TD><i> |</i></TR>\n<TR><i>| </i><TD>2</TD><i>    | </i><TD>Ganache-cli fork Hardhat fork</TD><i>                             | </i><TD>不支持fork</TD><i>                                                   | </i><TD>支持fork</TD><i>                                                     | </i><TD>无法在本地模拟OEC主网环境进行测试.</TD><i>              | </i><TD>建议直接在主网进行测试。</TD><i>                                     |</i></TR>\n<TR><i>| </i><TD>3.</TD><i>   | </i><TD>okexchain暂时不支持以太坊websockets中提供的batch call功能</TD><i> | </i><TD>正在开发中</TD><i>                                                   | </i><TD><URL url=\"https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/rpc/client.go#L323\">https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/rpc/client.go#L323</URL></TD><i> | </i><TD>批量调用websockets无法使用</TD><i>                      | </i><TD>okexchain添加支持该功能</TD><i>                                      |</i></TR>\n<TR><i>| </i><TD>4.</TD><i>   | </i><TD>okexchain交易哈希值与以太坊不兼容问题</TD><i> | </i><TD>okexchain上的交易哈希h2(amino编码+sha256哈希)跟cosmos风格相同</TD><i>                   | </i><TD>以太坊风格的交易哈希h(rlp编码+keccak256哈希)</TD><i> | </i><TD>Transaction hash mismatch from Provider.sendTransaction.</TD><i>                      | </i><TD><URL url=\"https://forum.okt.club/d/111-okexchain\">https://forum.okt.club/d/111-okexchain</URL></TD><i>                                      |</i></TR>\n<TR><i>| </i><TD>5.</TD><i>   | </i><TD>rest api 也不完全兼容</TD><i> | </i><TD><URL url=\"https://exchainrpc.okex.org/docs/en/#overview\">https://exchainrpc.okex.org/docs/en/#overview</URL></TD><i>                   |  </i><TD><URL url=\"https://etherscan.io/apidocs\">https://etherscan.io/apidocs</URL>   <URL url=\"https://github.com/EverexIO/Ethplorer/wiki/ethplorer-api\">https://github.com/EverexIO/Ethplorer/wiki/ethplorer-api</URL>   <URL url=\"https://www.blockcypher.com/dev/ethereum/#introduction\">https://www.blockcypher.com/dev/ethereum/#introduction</URL></TD><i>   |                      </i><TD/><i>|      </i><TD>分开调用</TD><i>                                 |</i></TR></TBODY></TABLE></r>', '2022-03-23 09:45:04', 1, NULL, NULL, '103.35.74.167', 0, 1, 0, 0),
