(327, 141, 1, '2021-08-04 07:36:36', 3, 'comment', '<r><H3><s>### </s>Introduction</H3>\n\n<p>ExOracle is an on-chain oracle. It provides various types of off-chain data for projects on the chain, including but not limited to the prices of various digital assets, such as BTC-USD. ExOracle  is implemented by the Solidity contract deployed on the EVM. Other projects on the chain can interact with the ExOracle to obtain the latest relevant price data. The price feeder can also provide the latest data to the ExOracle for earning some rewards.</p>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>Architecture</H3>\n\n<p>There are mainly four roles:</p>\n\n<LIST type=\"decimal\"><LI><s>1.  </s><p>ExOracle: <br/>\nThe ExOracle maintains the price data from all the feeders, and the ExOracle also determines who has the access to obtain the price.</p></LI>\n<LI><s>2. </s><p>Data Source:</p>\n\n    <p>Anyone can be the data source,and there is no barrier to become a data source.<br/>\n    The only thing the data source needs to do is to provide an accurate price and use the private key to sign data in a standard protocal.<br/>\n    As long as the data from a data source is provided to the chain by the price feeder, ExOracle will provide some credit rewards according to the address of the data source</p></LI>\n\n<LI><s>3. </s><p>Feeder:<br/>\nThe data feeder gets price data from a specific data source, then put it on the ExOracle. It will get some credit, even with some tokens supported from data caller.</p></LI>\n<LI><s>4. </s><p>Data Requester:<br/>\nGenerally speaking, most of Defi projects are Data Requester. If it want to obtain data from the ExOracle, it need to get the reading access from ExOracle authorization.</p></LI></LIST>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>code example</H3>\n\n<CODE lang=\"jsx\"><s>```jsx</s><i>\n</i>pragma solidity ^0.5.17;\npragma experimental ABIEncoderV2;\n\ninterface ICableOraclePriceData\n{\n    function registerRequesterViewer() external;\n    function put(bytes calldata message, bytes calldata signature) external returns (string memory);\n    function put(bytes[] calldata messages, bytes[] calldata signatures) external returns (string[] memory keys);\n    function latestRoundData(string calldata priceType, address dataSource) external view returns (uint80 roundId, int256 answer, uint256 startedAt, uint256 updatedAt, uint80 answeredInRound);\n    function get(string calldata priceType, address source) external view returns (uint256 price, uint256 timestamp);\n    function getOffchain(string calldata priceType, address source) external view returns (uint256 price, uint256 timestamp);\n    function getCumulativePrice(string calldata priceType, address source) external view returns (uint256 cumulativePrice,uint32 timestamp);\n    function changeSourceRecipient(address _recipient) external;\n    function changeFeederRecipient(address _recipient) external;\n    function postMining(address requester, bytes calldata message, bytes calldata signature) external;\n    function transferCredit(uint256 amount, address to) external;\n}\n\ncontract Demo {\n    address public exOracleAddress;\n    \n     /**\n     * Input an ExOracle contract address\n     */\n    constructor(address oracle) public {\n        exOracleAddress = oracle;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n     * @notice Read a single key from an authenticated source. \n     * @param priceType The selector for the value to return\n     * @param source The verifiable author of the data\n     */\n    function getLatestPrice(string memory priceType, address source) public view returns (uint256) \n    {\n        ICableOraclePriceData oracle = ICableOraclePriceData(exOracleAddress);\n        (uint256  value, uint256 timestamp) = oracle.get(priceType, source);\n        return value;\n    }\n    \n    /**\n    * @notice A specific example to get BTC-USD price\n    */\n    function getBtcPrice() public view returns (uint256) \n    {\n        address dataSource = 0x41f9950D778425D7B47619e0ad92117E1933918F;\n        return getLatestPrice(\"BTC\", dataSource);\n    }\n}<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>Deploy Information</H3>\n<p>All price messages are decoded in open oracle standard protocal, round to 6 decimal places</p>\n<LIST><LI><s>- </s><p>Mainnet ExOracle: <STRONG><s>**</s>0x31b820da47b4ebad81f653fdf32952d1bc1bc469<e>**</e></STRONG></p>\n    <LIST><LI><s>- </s><p>Median Datasource -10 minutes period: <STRONG><s>**</s>0x41f9950D778425D7B47619e0ad92117E1933918F<e>**</e></STRONG><br/>\n    support <STRONG><s>**</s>BTC、ETH、USDT、USDC、USDK、OKT、OKB、ONT、LTC、FIL、DAI、LINK 、SUSHI、UNI、DOT、ETC、WING、CHE<e>**</e></STRONG> with usd price</p>\n\n <p>Median Datasource from: OKEX usd Index、Coinbase usd Index、Coingecko、FTX、CoinMarketCap、CryptoCompare、Nomics，get price from these 7 plantfrom api and caculate the median price（Remove the maximum and minimum price, and then average）<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-12-16/1639625074-565929-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-12-16/1639625074-565929-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p></LI>\n\n    <LI><s>- </s><p>Datasource OKEx - 5 minutes period: <STRONG><s>**</s>0x85615B076615317C80F14cBad6501eec031cD51C<e>**</e></STRONG><br/>\n    support <STRONG><s>**</s>BTC、ETH<e>**</e></STRONG> with usdt quote price</p></LI>\n    <LI><s>- </s><p>Datasource Coinbase - 5 minutes period: <STRONG><s>**</s>0xfCEAdAFab14d46e20144F48824d0C09B1a03F2BC<e>**</e></STRONG><br/>\n    support <STRONG><s>**</s>BTC、ETH<e>**</e></STRONG> with usdt quote price</p></LI></LIST></LI>\n\n<LI><s>- </s><p>Testnet ExOracle: <STRONG><s>**</s>0x319b07E94eA8288aC0c15b4A24d26577Bec05366<e>**</e></STRONG></p>\n    <LIST><LI><s>- </s>Median Datasource - 10 minutes period: 0x41f9950D778425D7B47619e0ad92117E1933918F<br/>\nsupport BTC、ETH、USDT、USDC、USDK、OKT、OKB、ONT、LTC、FIL、DAI、LINK 、SUSHI、UNI、DOT、ETC、WING、CHE with usd price</LI></LIST></LI></LIST></r>', '2022-03-10 02:56:18', 33, NULL, NULL, '103.35.74.167', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(328, 142, 1, '2021-08-04 09:47:24', 28, 'comment', '<r><p>2021年7月30日，AnySwap部署了OKC和BSC链间的跨链桥，上线了BNB、BUSD等数字资产, 24小时跨链金额超过6000万美元。同时也在AnySwap V3路由器部署了OKC与Ethereum、BSC、Fantom、Polygon间的跨链路由，并上线了数字资产USDT。</p>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>一、AnySwap V2如何实现资产在BSC和OKC之间的跨链交换？</H2>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>1. 钱包网络设置</H3>\n\n<p>需要为浏览器安装MetaMask，且为MetaMask设置BSC和OKC主网网络。具体设置参数如下所示。</p>\n\n<p>OKC网络设置：<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070477-707636-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070477-707636-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n<p>BSC网络设置：</p>\n<CENTER><s>[center]</s><p><UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070496-179058-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070496-179058-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p><e>[/center]</e></CENTER>\n\n\n<p>用户也可以通过chainlist.org 自动添加网络。</p>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>2.如何使资产从BSC跨链到OKC？</H3>\n\n<p>①打开网页，进入OKC跨链桥地址：</p>\n\n<p><URL url=\"https://oec.anyswap.exchange\">https://oec.anyswap.exchange</URL></p>\n\n<p>②单击左侧菜单中的“Bridge”；</p>\n\n<p>③在右上角连接Metamask钱包，并设置为BSC（BNB）主网网络；</p>\n\n<p>④在“From”输入栏下方代币选择处，点击下拉箭头，将出现一个代币选项列表，选择想要跨链的资产（以BNB为例）；</p>\n\n<p>⑤在“To”输出栏下方网络选择处，选择想要跨链到的网络，即OKC（OKT）主网网络；</p>\n\n<p>⑥在“From”输入栏下方横线处输入需要跨链的代币数量；</p>\n\n<p>⑦点击“Swap”按钮，页面跳转到确认页面；<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070513-894414-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070513-894414-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n\n<p>⑧在确认页面，单击“Confirm”，弹出 Metamask 窗口；</p>\n\n<p>⑨在Metamask 窗口，点击“确认”按钮，然后代币BNB就会被跨链到OKExChain链上。<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070543-791002-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070543-791002-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n\n<H3><s>### </s>3.如何使资产从OKC跨回到BSC？</H3>\n\n<p>仍以BNB为例，将BNB从OKC链跨回到BSC链，与将BNB从BSC链跨链到OKC链操作步骤类似。</p>\n\n<p>不同之处在于：</p>\n\n<p>①需要将右上角Metamask的网络配置为OKC（OKT）主网网络；</p>\n\n<p>②在“To”输出栏下方网络选择处，选择的跨链网络为BSC（BNB）主网网络。<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070555-98249-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070555-98249-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n\n<H2><s>## </s>二、AnySwap V3 Beta如何实现资产在Ethereum和OKC之间的跨链交换?</H2>\n\n<p>2021年6月4日，AnySwap 多链路由器V3 Beta主网上线，该多链路由器具有三个显著的特点和功能：非托管+安全多方计算MPC、原生兑换和多链路由器。多链路由器允许用户在任意两条链之间快速交换，使跨链更容易，交易费用更低。当前，AnySwap V3 Beta主网已上线Ethereum、BSC、Fantom、Polygon 和OKC等公链，以及二层网络Abitrum！</p>\n\n<p>在AnySwap V3 Beta中，资产在Ethereum与OKC链之间的跨链交换操作流程也适用于资产在BSC与OKC、Fantom与OKC、Polygon与OKC生态链之间的跨链交换，用户只需根据实际情况选择正确的网络与相应的资产即可。</p>\n\n<p>我们以资产在Ethereum与OKC链之间的跨链交换为例。</p>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>1.环境准备</H3>\n\n<p>需要为浏览器安装MetaMask，且为MetaMask设置OKC主网网络。具体设置参数如上一章节所示。</p>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>2.如何使资产从Ethereum跨链到OKC？</H3>\n\n<p>①打开网页，进入AnySwap V3跨链路由器地址：</p>\n\n<p><URL url=\"https://stable.anyswap.exchange\">https://stable.anyswap.exchange</URL></p>\n\n<p>②单击左侧菜单中的“Swap”；</p>\n\n<p>③在右上角连接Metamask钱包，并设置为Ethereum（ETH）主网网络；<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070574-842900-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070574-842900-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n<p>④在“From”输入栏下方代币选择处，点击下拉菜单，出现代币选项列表时，选择想要跨链的代币（以USDT为例）；<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070584-818652-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070584-818652-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n<p>⑤在“To”输出栏下方网络选择处，点击下拉菜单，出现网络选项列表时，选择需要跨链到的网络，即OKC（OKT）主网网络；<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070658-966928-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070658-966928-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n<p>⑥在“From”输入栏下方横线处输入需要跨链的代币数量；</p>\n\n<p>⑦单击“Swap”选项，然后会弹出Metamask窗口，最后单击“Confirm”按钮，然后代币USDT就会被跨链到OKExChain链上。<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070599-791365-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070599-791365-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>3.如何使资产从OKC跨回到Ethereum？</H3>\n\n<p>仍以USDT为例，将USDT从OKC链跨回到Ethereum链，与将USDT从Ethereum链跨链到OKC链操作步骤类似。</p>\n\n<p>不同之处在于：</p>\n\n<p>①需要将右上角Metamask的网络配置为OKC（OKT）主网网络；</p>\n\n<p>②在“To”输出栏下方网络选择处，点击下拉菜单，出现网络选项列表时，需要选择Ethereum（ETH）主网网络。<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070686-184388-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070686-184388-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n\n<H2><s>## </s>关于AnySwap：</H2>\n\n<p>AnySwap 是一个完全去中心化的跨链交换协议，该协议可以使用全球任一主流生态体系内的数字资产，直接兑换其他生态体系内的任何种类的数字资产，而不需要再通过其他工具或渠道作中介。目前AnySwap团队已经突破了基于ECDSA、EDDSA和SM2密码算法的SMPC安全多方计算+TSS门限签名技术，并完成了其工程化快速实现，使得 AnySwap跨链桥可以覆盖目前几乎全部种类数字资产。截至2021年8月4日，AnySwap锁定资产总量接近5亿美元，拥有31个节点，实现了18个公链生态的资产跨链转移，支持了458种数字资产。<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070698-900557-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-04/1628070698-900557-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n</r>', '2022-03-23 09:38:38', 1, NULL, NULL, '103.35.74.167', 0, 1, 0, 0),
