(350, 156, 1, '2021-08-07 07:31:21', 27, 'comment', '<r><H2><s>## </s>错误信息</H2>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>incompatible: peer is on a different network. Got okexchain-65, expected exchain-66 module=pex <i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<H2><s>## </s>原因</H2>\n<p>使用exchaind init时填写了okexchain-65，在exchaind start的时候又指定了exchain-66</p>\n\n\n<H2><s>## </s>解决办法<e>    </e></H2>\n<p>严格按主网、测试网文档执行，<br/>\n测试网节点搭建参考：<URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/testnets\">https://github.com/okx/testnets</URL><br/>\n主网节点搭建参考：<URL url=\"https://forum.okt.club/d/127-faq\">https://forum.okt.club/d/127-faq</URL>  <URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/mainnet\">https://github.com/okx/mainnet</URL><br/>\n<STRONG><s>**</s>不要把主网的~/.exchaind文件夹与测试网的混用。<e>**</e></STRONG></p></r>', '2021-08-09 06:17:46', 28, NULL, NULL, '43.245.196.166', 0, 1, 0, 0),
