(371, 168, 1, '2021-08-11 03:10:12', 32, 'comment', '<r><p>1.创建新工程，并创建main.go文件；<br/>\n2.在本工程根目录下，利用终端执行：<C><s>`</s>go mod init<e>`</e></C><br/>\n3.将最新的gosdk release 版本填进go.mod文件中:</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>module gosdk_demo\n\ngo 1.15\n\nrequire (\n	github.com/cosmos/cosmos-sdk v0.39.2\n	github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum v1.9.25\n	github.com/okx/exchain-go-sdk v0.18.2\n)\n\nreplace (\n	github.com/cosmos/cosmos-sdk =&gt; github.com/okx/cosmos-sdk v0.39.2-exchain3\n	github.com/tendermint/iavl =&gt; github.com/okx/iavl v0.14.3-exchain\n	github.com/tendermint/tendermint =&gt; github.com/okx/tendermint v0.33.9-exchain2\n)<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>4.终端相同路径执行：<C><s>`</s>go mod tidy<e>`</e></C><br/>\n5 编写main函数，在其中调用gosdk：</p>\n<CODE lang=\"go\"><s>```go</s><i>\n</i>package main\n\nimport (\n	\"fmt\"\n	\"log\"\n	\"math/big\"\n\n	sdk \"github.com/cosmos/cosmos-sdk/types\"\n	ethcmn \"github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/common\"\n	\"github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/core/types\"\n	\"github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/crypto\"\n	\"github.com/okx/exchain-go-sdk\"\n)\n\nconst (\n	// exchain testnet\'s rpc\n	rpcURL = \"https://exchaintesttmrpc.okex.org\"\n	// chain-id\n	testChainID = \"exchain-65\"\n)\n\nfunc main() {\n	chainID := big.NewInt(65)\n	privKey := \"17e95da01c05e58ef57deb25aa78f008bb8ebe8a173fa3a4eb64f8ed24abaf07\"\n	privateKeyECDSA, err := crypto.HexToECDSA(privKey)\n	if err != nil {\n		log.Fatalf(\"failed to switch unencrypted private key -&gt; secp256k1 private key: %+v\", err)\n	}\n\n	toAddressStr := \"0xd01bf1F0dB0E0F9998Ec01a45Cfc03116D0224bE\"\n	toAddress := ethcmn.HexToAddress(toAddressStr)\n\n	config, err := gosdk.NewClientConfig(rpcURL, testChainID, gosdk.BroadcastBlock, \"0.000000001okt\", 21000,\n		0, \"\")\n	if err != nil {\n		log.Fatalln(err)\n	}\n	cli := gosdk.NewClient(config)\n	value, err := sdk.NewDecFromStr(\"1\")\n	if err != nil {\n		log.Fatalln(err)\n	}\n	gasPrice, err := sdk.NewDecFromStr(\"0.000000001\")\n	if err != nil {\n		log.Fatalln(err)\n	}\n\n	unsignedTx := types.NewTransaction(25, toAddress, value.BigInt(), 21000, gasPrice.BigInt(), nil)\n	signedTx, err := types.SignTx(unsignedTx, types.NewEIP155Signer(chainID), privateKeyECDSA)\n	if err != nil {\n		log.Fatalf(\"failed to sign the unsignedTx offline: %+v\", err)\n	}\n	hash, err := cli.Evm().GetTxHash(signedTx)\n	if err != nil {\n		log.Fatalln(err)\n	}\n	// check txHash on: https://www.oklink.com/okexchain-test/tx/0x8f7678deec49b928d6b0dfc06e6de0700f8bdbb90995e085756f7c8764d31337\n	fmt.Println(hash)\n}<i>\n\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>6.编译并执行，如图：<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-11/1628653257-959886-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-08-11/1628653257-959886-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n</r>', '2021-08-11 03:48:13', 32, NULL, NULL, '103.35.74.167', 0, 1, 0, 0),
