(435, 195, 1, '2021-08-25 08:03:08', 34, 'comment', '<r><H2><s>## </s>背景：</H2>\n<LIST type=\"decimal\"><LI><s>1. </s>OKC测试网在高度<C><s>`</s>5300000<e>`</e></C>高度后不再支持homestead签名，<COLOR color=\"red\"><s>[color=red]</s>仅支持EIP155签名</COLOR></LI>\n<LI><s>2. </s>OKC主网在高度<C><s>`</s>5150000<e>`</e></C>高度后不再支持homestead签名，<COLOR color=\"red\"><s>[color=red]</s>仅支持EIP155签名</COLOR></LI>\n<LI><s>3. </s>EIP155签名消息中应明确指定<C><s>`</s>chainId<e>`</e></C>, 参考<URL url=\"https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-155\"><s>[</s>链接<e>](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-155)</e></URL></LI></LIST>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>问题：</H2>\n<p>发送homestead签名交易会报如下错误：</p>\n<CODE lang=\"language\"><s>```language</s><i>\n</i>SetFail: dot unauthorized: signature verification failed: deprecated support for homestead Signer<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<H2><s>## </s>解决方案：</H2>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>1. we3js开发者(以主网为例)</H3>\n<LIST type=\"decimal\"><LI><s>1. </s>指定chainId对交易进行签名，会输出<C><s>`</s>rawTransaction<e>`</e></C>\n<CODE lang=\"JavaScript\"><s>```JavaScript</s><i>\n</i>const web3 = require(\'web3\');\nconst Web3 = new web3(new web3.providers.HttpProvider(\'https://exchainrpc.okex.org\'));\nWeb3.eth.accounts.signTransaction({\n    to: \'0xF0109fC8DF283027b6285cc889F5aA624EaC1F55\',\n    value: \'1000000000\',\n    gas: 2000000,\n    gasPrice: \'234567897654321\',\n    nonce: 100,\n    chainId: 66\n}, \'your-private-key\')\n    .then(console.log);<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE></LI>\n<LI><s>2. </s>将上面签名后的<C><s>`</s>rawTransaction<e>`</e></C>广播到主网中\n<CODE lang=\"JavaScript\"><s>```JavaScript</s><i>\n</i>web3.eth.sendSignedTransaction(\'rawTransaction\').on(\'receipt\', console.log);<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE></LI>\n<LI><s>3. </s>参考链接:\n   <LIST type=\"decimal\"><LI><s>1. </s><URL url=\"https://web3js.readthedocs.io/en/v1.4.0/web3-eth-accounts.html#signtransaction\">https://web3js.readthedocs.io/en/v1.4.0/web3-eth-accounts.html#signtransaction</URL></LI>      </LIST></LI></LIST>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>2. truffle开发者</H3>\n\n<LIST type=\"decimal\"><LI><s>1. </s><p>使用<C><s>`</s>v5.1.42<e>`</e></C>或以上版本的truffle；依赖的hdwallet-provider package建议使用<br/>\n<C><s>`</s>\"@truffle/hdwallet-provider\": \"^1.2.3\"<e>`</e></C></p></LI>\n\n<LI><s>2. </s><p>需要将truffle-config.js中的<C><s>`</s>require(\'truffle-hdwallet-provider\')<e>`</e></C>改为<C><s>`</s>require(\'@truffle/hdwallet-provider\')<e>`</e></C>，代码中其他地方的引用也需要修改</p></LI></LIST></r>', '2022-09-26 06:16:47', 34, NULL, NULL, '120.245.120.143', 0, 1, 0, 0),
