(453, 203, 1, '2021-09-02 08:42:15', 28, 'comment', '<r>\n<p>目前，暂只支持使用GitHub账户登录。</p>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>1. 注册</H2>\n<p>点击论坛右上角Sign Up，如图所示：<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-02/1630572263-755951-1.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-02/1630572263-755951-1.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW><br/>\n在弹窗中选择第二个\"Log In with GitHub\"，如图所示：<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-02/1630572128-610746-a47e07a3-6e4f-4107-bfca-53855ee2fddf.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-02/1630572128-610746-a47e07a3-6e4f-4107-bfca-53855ee2fddf.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW><br/>\n此时会再次弹窗，在新的弹窗中输入GitHub账号和密码，单击确认就注册成功了。</p>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>2. 登录</H2>\n<p><UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-02/1630572447-111448-1.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-02/1630572447-111448-1.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n<p><UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-02/1630572128-610746-a47e07a3-6e4f-4107-bfca-53855ee2fddf.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-02/1630572128-610746-a47e07a3-6e4f-4107-bfca-53855ee2fddf.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW><br/>\n正常情况下，只要登录过一次之后，就会记住登录状态，下次就可以直接登录了。</p>\n\n<p>其他登录方式，正在解决中。<br/>\n解决后会在第一时间更新注册登录方式。</p>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>3. 如何发帖</H2>\n<p>帖子格式须使用markdown格式，以背景，问题，解决方案作为模板输出，具体参考：<URL url=\"https://forum.okt.club/d/254-evm-trace\">https://forum.okt.club/d/254-evm-trace</URL></p>\n<LIST><LI><s>- </s><p>方式1，直接在首页点击\"发布主题\"<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2022-01-04/1641269013-597048-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2022-01-04/1641269013-597048-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW><br/>\n在点击后出现的弹窗中，选择标签板块，写标题和内容，再点击保存，帖子即发布成功。<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2022-01-04/1641269261-942862-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2022-01-04/1641269261-942862-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p></LI>\n\n<LI><s>- </s><p>方式2，先进入一个板块，比如 开发者|dev，进入后，点击左侧的\"发布主题\"<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2022-01-04/1641269341-289929-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2022-01-04/1641269341-289929-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW><br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2022-01-04/1641269417-271980-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2022-01-04/1641269417-271980-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p></LI></LIST>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>4. 如何修改帖子</H2>\n<p>如下图所示，在帖子的右下角点击三个点，在弹窗中选择编辑，即计入编辑状态。修改完毕，点击发布，即保存生效<br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2022-01-04/1641269453-943827-origin-img-v2-6f46223a-9afd-443a-b4d2-b8cc54160c3h.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2022-01-04/1641269453-943827-origin-img-v2-6f46223a-9afd-443a-b4d2-b8cc54160c3h.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n\n\n\n\n</r>', '2022-01-04 04:24:25', 34, NULL, NULL, '43.245.196.166', 0, 1, 0, 0),
