(458, 206, 1, '2021-09-04 00:40:10', 28, 'comment', '<r><H1><s># </s>背景：</H1>\n<p>validator节点是OEC网络正常运行的关键节点，是网络畅通的基本保障。</p>\n\n<H1><s># </s>问题：</H1>\n<p>如何查看validator节点运行状态？<br/>\n当validator节点被jailed之后，执行什么命令能快速接触jailed？</p>\n\n<H1><s># </s>解决方案：</H1>\n\n<p>OEC有0x和ex开头两种格式的地址。他们的区别和相互转换，详细请查阅 <URL url=\"https://forum.okt.club/d/54-ex0x\"><s>[</s>此处<e>](https://forum.okt.club/d/54-ex0x)</e></URL>。</p>\n\n\n<H2><s>## </s>1. 如何获取validator的oper地址，共识地址，共识公钥，p2p连接的node-id</H2>\n<H4><s>#### </s>查看validator的exvaloper开头的地址</H4>\n<p>方式1：在你执行create-validator成功的时候，会显示</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>    {\n      \"type\": \"okexchain/staking/MsgCreateValidator\",\n      \"value\": {\n        \"description\": {\n          \"moniker\": \"my nickname\",\n          \"identity\": \"logo|||http://mywebsite/pic/logo.jpg\",\n          \"website\": \"http://mywebsite\",\n          \"details\": \"my slogan\"\n        },\n        \"min_self_delegation\": {\n          \"denom\": \"okt\",\n          \"amount\": \"10000.000000000000000000\"\n        },\n        \"delegator_address\": \"exXXX\",\n        \"validator_address\": \"exvaloperXXX\",\n        \"pubkey\": \"exvalconspubXXX\"\n      }\n    }<i>\n</i><e>    ```</e></CODE>\n<p>方式2：通过rest api接口<br/>\n<URL url=\"https://www.okex.com/okexchain/v1/staking/address/B8586789B5681169A6CDC670775AC83FF560AA2F/validator_address\">https://www.okex.com/okexchain/v1/staking/address/B8586789B5681169A6CDC670775AC83FF560AA2F/validator_address</URL><br/>\n注：参数中B8586XXX是公钥地址，他们之间的互转可以参考<URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/exchain-java-sdk\"><s>[</s>JavaSDK<e>](https://github.com/okx/exchain-java-sdk)</e></URL>中的相关方法。</p>\n\n<H4><s>#### </s>查看validator的共识地址，以exvalcons开头</H4>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>exchaind tendermint show-address --home {$HOME}<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<H4><s>#### </s>查看validator的共识公钥，以exvalconspub开头</H4>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>exchaind tendermint show-validator --home {$HOME}<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<H4><s>#### </s>查看validator的用于p2p互连的node_id</H4>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>exchaind tendermint show-node-id --home {$HOME}<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>2. 如何查看validator节点运行状态</H2>\n<H4><s>#### </s>查看当前节点状态信息</H4>\n<p>方式1：通过命令行查看</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>exchaincli query staking validator {exvaloper地址} --node https://exchaintmrpc.okex.org<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>例如：</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>{\n  \"operator_address\": \"exvaloperXXX\",\n  \"consensus_pubkey\": {\n    \"type\": \"tendermint/PubKeyEd25519\",\n    \"value\": \"tAsQ7uiPQds/kyGUdiHXncrLr6Frd+pzpq/goSkjTyc=\"\n  },\n  \"jailed\": false,\n  \"status\": 2,\n  \"delegator_shares\": \"9022111028969.393322378207128679\",\n  \"description\": {\n    \"moniker\": \"Collector\",\n    \"identity\": \"\",\n    \"website\": \"\",\n    \"details\": \"\"\n  },\n  \"unbonding_height\": \"0\",\n  \"unbonding_time\": \"2021-02-17T01:49:59.985069599Z\",\n  \"min_self_delegation\": \"10000.000000000000000000\"\n}<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>方式2：通过rest api查看：<br/>\n<URL url=\"https://www.okex.com/okexchain/v1/staking/validators/%7Bexvaloper%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80\">https://www.okex.com/okexchain/v1/staking/validators/{exvaloper地址</URL>}  <br/>\n例如：</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>{\n    operator_address: \"exvaloperXXX\",\n    consensus_pubkey: \"exvalconspubXXX\",\n    jailed: false,\n    status: 2,\n    tokens: \"0\",\n    delegator_shares: \"9026049898354.118251952618490392\",\n    description: {\n        moniker: \"Zapzap\",\n        identity: \"\",\n        website: \"\",\n        details: \"\"\n    },\n    unbonding_height: \"0\",\n    unbonding_time: \"1970-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n    commission: {\n        commission_rates: {\n            rate: \"1.000000000000000000\",    \n            max_rate: \"1.000000000000000000\",\n            max_change_rate: \"0.000000000000000000\"\n        },\n        update_time: \"1970-01-01T00:00:00Z\"\n    },\n    min_self_delegation: \"10000.000000000000000000\"\n}<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>其中参数<C><s>`</s>jailed: false<e>`</e></C>表示节点是正常状态；<C><s>`</s>jailed: true<e>`</e></C>表示当前节点处于被惩罚状态，此时不能参与出块。此时要先解除惩罚状态，再下一轮竞选周期中再次参与出块。</p>\n<H4><s>#### </s>查看validator的签名信息</H4>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>exchaincli query slashing signing-info {exvalconpub地址} --node https://exchaintmrpc.okex.org  --trust-node=true<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>例如：<br/>\naddress: exvalconsXX<br/>\nstart_height: 0<br/>\nindex_offset: 45583<br/>\njailed_until: 2021-09-01T09:16:54.483366695Z<br/>\ntombstoned: false<br/>\nmissed_blocks_counter: 5<br/>\nvalidator_status: 0<br/>\n其中<C><s>`</s>missed_blocks_counter: 5<e>`</e></C> 表示错过出块次数5次，一般情况下，次数过多会被jailed。</p>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>3. 如何解除jailed受惩罚状态</H2>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>exchaincli tx slashing unjail --from jack --fees 0.0005okt --chain-id=exchain-66 --node https://exchaintmrpc.okex.org<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>其中：jack是validator的名称。</p>\n\n<H4><s>#### </s>查看validator当前的惩罚参数标准</H4>\n\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>exchaincli query slashing params  --node https://exchaintmrpc.okex.org  --trust-node=true<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n</r>', '2021-09-05 12:52:33', 28, NULL, NULL, '43.245.196.166', 0, 1, 0, 0),
