(501, 232, 1, '2021-09-23 03:38:22', 3, 'comment', '<r><H2><s>## </s>背景</H2>\n<p>推荐几个智能合约开发中总会用到的的一些便捷小工具，方便开发过程中突然需要算个东西没工具使用。都是亲测可用的。</p>\n<H2><s>## </s>网页小工具</H2>\n<LIST><LI><s>- </s><p>以太坊Keccak-256网页工具，快速计算hash或者合约函数id  <URL url=\"https://emn178.github.io/online-tools/keccak_256.html\">https://emn178.github.io/online-tools/keccak_256.html</URL><br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-23/1632368782-569550-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-23/1632368782-569550-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p></LI>\n\n<LI><s>- </s><p>ABI Encoding,输入abi json就可以选择合约函数输入参数，得到合约调用对应data  <URL url=\"https://abi.hashex.org\">https://abi.hashex.org</URL><br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-23/1632368910-377529-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-23/1632368910-377529-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p></LI>\n\n<LI><s>- </s><p>以太坊tx的data解析 <URL url=\"https://lab.miguelmota.com/ethereum-input-data-decoder/example/\">https://lab.miguelmota.com/ethereum-input-data-decoder/example/</URL><br/>\n<UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW url=\"https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-23/1632368941-63650-image.png\">[upl-image-preview url=https://forum.okt.club/assets/files/2021-09-23/1632368941-63650-image.png]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p></LI></LIST>\n</r>', '2021-09-23 03:49:56', 3, NULL, NULL, '103.35.74.167', 0, 1, 0, 0),
