(510, 235, 1, '2021-09-26 01:46:32', 38, 'comment', '<r><H1><s># </s>背景<e> </e></H1>\n<p>在exchain node运行过程中，会偶尔出现节点程序退出的情况，致使无法继续出块，节点退出网络。</p>\n\n<H1><s># </s>问题</H1>\n<p>对这种情况我们该从哪些方面调查以定位问题原因呢？</p>\n\n<H1><s># </s>解决方案</H1>\n<H2><s>## </s>一、以进程方式启动的节点</H2>\n<H3><s>### </s>1. 确认节点程序运行状态</H3>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>ps -ef | grep exchaind<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<H3><s>### </s>2. 查看node log</H3>\n<p>node log文件在<C><s>`</s>--log_file<e>`</e></C>指定的目录下，如果未指定，则默认在<C><s>`</s>--home<e>`</e></C>目录中。当然你也可能使用stdout将log输出到某个文件了。</p>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>tail {{log_file}}<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>如果log输出内容中有Panic相关信息，则可据此定位问题。</p>\n<H3><s>### </s>3. 查看系统log（因系统而异）</H3>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>## ubuntu\ncat /var/log/syslog \n## centos\ncat /var/log/messages<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>如果怀疑是OOM，则可直接过滤oom信息</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>## ubuntu\ncat /var/log/syslog | grep oom\n## centos\ncat /var/log/messages ｜ grep oom<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>如果节点因OOM退出，则会输出如下信息：<br/>\n<STRONG><s>**</s>ubuntu<e>**</e></STRONG></p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>Sep 25 12:00:08 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: [188473.255863] exchaind invoked oom-killer: gfp_mask=0x100cca(GFP_HIGHUSER_MOVABLE), order=0, oom_score_adj=0\nSep 25 12:00:08 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: [188473.255881]  oom_kill_process+0xe6/0x120\nSep 25 12:00:08 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: [188473.255996] [  pid  ]   uid  tgid total_vm      rss pgtables_bytes swapents oom_score_adj name\nSep 25 12:00:08 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: [188473.256088] oom-kill:constraint=CONSTRAINT_NONE,nodemask=(null),cpuset=3162a4f5ac3a0f2729b4818685d58f19b8492bc4b04bfc9931e310d798b6b68f,mems_allowed=0,global_oom,task_memcg=/docker/3162a4f5ac3a0f2729b4818685d58f19b8492bc4b04bfc9931e310d798b6b68f,task=exchaind,pid=5303,uid=0\nSep 25 12:00:08 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: [188473.256127] Out of memory: Killed process 5303 (exchaind) total-vm:16892996kB, anon-rss:15551640kB, file-rss:0kB, shmem-rss:0kB, UID:0 pgtables:31604kB oom_score_adj:0\nSep 25 12:00:09 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: [188474.079316] oom_reaper: reaped process 5303 (exchaind), now anon-rss:0kB, file-rss:0kB, shmem-rss:0kB<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p><STRONG><s>**</s>centos<e>**</e></STRONG></p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>Aug 30 23:27:32 okchain-1 kernel: YDEdr invoked oom-killer: gfp_mask=0x201da, order=0, oom_score_adj=0\nAug 30 23:27:32 okchain-1 kernel: [&lt;ffffffff88bc251e&gt;] oom_kill_process+0x25e/0x3f0\nAug 30 23:27:32 okchain-1 kernel: [&lt;ffffffff88bc1f7d&gt;] ? oom_unkillable_task+0xcd/0x120\nAug 30 23:27:32 okchain-1 kernel: [ pid ]   uid  tgid total_vm      rss nr_ptes swapents oom_score_adj name\nSep 16 11:12:16 okchain-1 kernel: exchaind invoked oom-killer: gfp_mask=0x280da, order=0, oom_score_adj=0\nSep 16 11:12:16 okchain-1 kernel: [&lt;ffffffff9b3c251e&gt;] oom_kill_process+0x25e/0x3f0\nSep 16 11:12:16 okchain-1 kernel: [&lt;ffffffff9b3c1f7d&gt;] ? oom_unkillable_task+0xcd/0x120\nSep 16 11:12:16 okchain-1 kernel: [ pid ]   uid  tgid total_vm      rss nr_ptes swapents oom_score_adj name\nSep 20 01:00:54 okchain-1 kernel: exchaind invoked oom-killer: gfp_mask=0x280da, order=0, oom_score_adj=0\nSep 20 01:00:55 okchain-1 kernel: [&lt;ffffffff8f9c251e&gt;] oom_kill_process+0x25e/0x3f0\nSep 20 01:00:55 okchain-1 kernel: [&lt;ffffffff8f9c1f7d&gt;] ? oom_unkillable_task+0xcd/0x120\nSep 20 01:00:55 okchain-1 kernel: [ pid ]   uid  tgid total_vm      rss nr_ptes swapents oom_score_adj name<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<H2><s>## </s>二、以容器方式启动的节点</H2>\n<H3><s>### </s>1. 确认节点容器运行状态</H3>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>docker ps -a<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<H3><s>### </s>2. 查看node log</H3>\n<p>node log文件在<C><s>`</s>--log_file<e>`</e></C>指定的目录下，如果未指定，则默认在<C><s>`</s>--home<e>`</e></C>目录中。当然你也可能使用stdout将log输出到某个文件了。</p>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>tail {{log_file}}<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>如果log输出内容中有Panic相关信息，则可据此定位问题。</p>\n<H3><s>### </s>3. 查看容器log</H3>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>docker logs {{container_name}}<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>log中如果有Panic信息，则可据此定位问题。</p>\n<H3><s>### </s>4. 查看容器状态</H3>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>docker inspect {{container_name}}<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>输出类似以下内容</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i> \"State\": {\n            \"Status\": \"exited\",\n            \"Running\": false,\n            \"Paused\": false,\n            \"Restarting\": false,\n            \"OOMKilled\": false,\n            \"Dead\": false,\n            \"Pid\": 0,\n            \"ExitCode\": 137,\n            \"Error\": \"\",\n            \"StartedAt\": \"2021-09-23T08:07:57.700894586Z\",\n            \"FinishedAt\": \"2021-09-25T12:00:09.111199614Z\"\n        },<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>据此可判断是否为<C><s>`</s>OOMKilled<e>`</e></C>以及<C><s>`</s>ExitCode<e>`</e></C>。</p>\n<H3><s>### </s>5. 查看docker deamon log</H3>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>journalctl -k | tail -n 30<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>输出内容中通常会有容器退出信息，如下</p>\n<CODE><s>```</s><i>\n</i>Sep 25 12:00:08 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: oom-kill:constraint=CONSTRAINT_NONE,nodemask=(null),cpuset=3162a4f5ac3a0f2729b4818685d58f19b8492bc4b04bfc9931e310d798b6b68f,mems_allowed=0,global_oom,task_memcg=/docker/3162a4f5ac3a0f2729b4818685d58f19b8492bc4b04bfc9931e310d798b6b68f,task=exchaind,pid=5303,uid=0\nSep 25 12:00:08 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: Out of memory: Killed process 5303 (exchaind) total-vm:16892996kB, anon-rss:15551640kB, file-rss:0kB, shmem-rss:0kB, UID:0 pgtables:31604kB oom_score_adj:0\nSep 25 12:00:09 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: oom_reaper: reaped process 5303 (exchaind), now anon-rss:0kB, file-rss:0kB, shmem-rss:0kB\nSep 25 12:00:10 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: br-c318f95130ae: port 1(vethbade7b0) entered disabled state\nSep 25 12:00:10 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: vethf51c9ff: renamed from eth0\nSep 25 12:00:10 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: br-c318f95130ae: port 1(vethbade7b0) entered disabled state\nSep 25 12:00:10 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: device vethbade7b0 left promiscuous mode\nSep 25 12:00:10 ip-172-31-38-25 kernel: br-c318f95130ae: port 1(vethbade7b0) entered disabled state<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n</r>', '2021-09-27 03:57:04', 38, NULL, NULL, '43.245.222.33', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(511, 236, 1, '2021-09-26 03:17:39', 28, 'comment', '<r><TABLE><THEAD><TR><i>| </i><TH align=\"left\"/><i>|</i><TH align=\"left\">超级节点</TH><i>|</i><TH align=\"left\">全节点</TH><i>|</i><TH align=\"left\">归档节点</TH><i>|</i></TR></THEAD><i>\n|:----|:----|:----|:----|</i>\n<TBODY><TR><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">CPU</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">16核，主频3.5GHz或以上</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">16核，主频建议3GHz或以上</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">16核，主频建议3GHz或以上</TD><i>|</i></TR>\n<TR><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">系统类型</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">x86_64</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">x86_64</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">x86_64</TD><i>|</i></TR>\n<TR><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">内存</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">64G</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">64G</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">128G</TD><i>|</i></TR>\n<TR><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">磁盘</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">1T SSD云盘</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">1T SSD云盘</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">5T SSD云盘(且可扩展)</TD><i>|</i></TR>\n<TR><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">带宽</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">100M</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">100M</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">100M</TD><i>|</i></TR>\n<TR><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">强烈建议</TD><i>|</i><TD align=\"left\">AWS m6i.4xlarge 16核64G 主频3.5GHz</TD><i>| </i><TD align=\"left\">AWS m6i.4xlarge</TD><i> | </i><TD align=\"left\">AWS r6i.4xlarge</TD><i> |</i></TR></TBODY></TABLE>\n\n\n\n<H1><s># </s>运行节点的磁盘建议</H1>\n<H2><s>## </s>背景</H2>\n<p>OEC节点使用level db存储区块数据和状态数据，会频繁读取磁盘，对磁盘性能要求比较高。</p>\n<H2><s>## </s>问题</H2>\n<p>使用阿里云的普通云盘，会导致节点同步区块落后。</p>\n<H2><s>## </s>解决方法</H2>\n<p>阿里云有4款云盘类型：普通云盘、高效云盘、SSD云盘和ESSD云盘，建议使用SSD云盘。<br/>\naws机器也建议使用ssd类型云盘。</p>\n\n<p>备注：阿里云磁盘说明参考 <URL url=\"https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/25383.html\">https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/25383.html</URL></p></r>', '2022-12-21 00:15:57', 28, NULL, NULL, '103.35.74.167', 0, 1, 0, 0),
