(516, 240, 1, '2021-10-15 09:21:08', 152, 'comment', '<r><p>I\'ve started my node this way:</p>\n\n<p>exchaind start --chain-id exchain-66 --mempool.sort_tx_by_gp --home /home/ubuntu/.exchaind --wsport 8546</p>\n\n<p>If I try this:</p>\n\n<p>curl -X POST --data \'{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"web3_clientVersion\",\"params\":[],\"id\":67}\' -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" <URL url=\"http://localhost:26657\">http://localhost:26657</URL></p>\n\n<p>I receive this:</p>\n\n<p>{<br/>\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",<br/>\n  \"id\": 67,<br/>\n  \"error\": {<br/>\n    \"code\": -32601,<br/>\n    \"message\": \"Method not found\"<br/>\n  }<br/>\n}</p>\n\n<p>How can I use the RPC methods?</p>\n</r>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '217.216.113.24', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(518, 242, 1, '2021-10-20 09:11:38', 28, 'comment', '<r><H1><s># </s>背景</H1>\n<p>自<URL url=\"https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/tag/v0.19.12.2\"><s>[</s>v0.19.12.2<e>](https://github.com/okx/exchain/releases/tag/v0.19.12.2)</e></URL>版本起，OEC使用的leveldb被改为性能更好的rocksdb。</p>\n\n<H1><s># </s>问题</H1>\n<p>当前leveldb格式的数据，如何操作才能转换为rocksdb格式<br/>\n如何直接启动一个rocksdb数据格式的节点<br/>\n如何基于rocksdb格式的数据快照，启动一个新节点</p>\n\n<H1><s># </s>解决办法</H1>\n<H2><s>## </s>1. 更新代码</H2>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i># 注意版本 $version ≥ v0.19.12.2\ngit clone -b $version https://github.com/okx/exchain.git \ncd exchain<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n\n\n<H2><s>## </s>2. <URL url=\"https://forum.okt.club/d/267-rocksdb\"><s>[</s>安装 rocksdb<e>](https://forum.okt.club/d/267-rocksdb)</e></URL></H2>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>3. 编译 exchaind</H2>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i># 编译支持 rocksdb 的 exchaind\nmake mainnet WITH_ROCKSDB=true<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p><COLOR color=\"red\"><s>[color=red]</s><br/>\n注：务必要指定: <C><s>`</s>WITH_ROCKSDB=true<e>`</e></C><br/>\n<e>[/color]</e></COLOR></p>\n\n<H4><s>#### </s>如果编译过程中报错，尝试运行如下命令：</H4>\n<p>先切换到dev分支，执行make rocksdb，再执行exchaind：make mainnet WITH_ROCKSDB=true</p>\n<LIST type=\"decimal\"><LI><s>1. </s>yum install -y -q  git make snappy snappy-devel lz4-devel yum-utils</LI>\n<LI><s>2. </s>git clone <URL url=\"https://github.com/facebook/rocksdb.git\">https://github.com/facebook/rocksdb.git</URL> -b v6.15.5</LI>\n<LI><s>3. </s>cd rocksdb</LI>\n<LI><s>4. </s>make uninstall PREFIX=/usr LIBDIR=/usr/lib</LI>\n<LI><s>5. </s>make shared_lib PREFIX=/usr LIBDIR=/usr/lib</LI>\n<LI><s>6. </s>make install-shared PREFIX=/usr LIBDIR=/usr/lib</LI>\n<LI><s>7. </s>ldconfig</LI></LIST>\n\n\n\n<H2><s>## </s>4. 有3种方法获得rocksdb格式的区块数据</H2>\n<H3><s>### </s>a. 把 leveldb格式的数据转换为 rocksdb 格式</H3>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>exchaind data convert --home ${oec-node-home}<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p>命令执行成功后，原${oec-node-home}/data/中的所有*.db由leveldb格式转换为rocksdb格式. 原始的leveldb格式数据保存在${oec-node-home}/data_backup中。<br/>\n注：convert命令执行需要一定时长，转换速度48g/h左右。</p>\n\n<p>如需了解转换命令<C><s>`</s>convert<e>`</e></C>更多 <URL url=\"https://forum.okt.club/d/243-oec-leveldbrocksdb\"><s>[</s>参见此处<e>](https://forum.okt.club/d/243-oec-leveldbrocksdb)</e></URL>。</p>\n\n  <br/>\n<H3><s>### </s>b. 使用rocksdb格式的快照</H3>\n<p><URL url=\"https://forum.okt.club/d/154\"><s>[</s>快照链接<e>](https://forum.okt.club/d/154)</e></URL></p>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>rm -rf ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/data\ncd ${EXCHAIND_PATH}\nwget https://ok-public-hk.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/cdn/okexchain/snapshot/okexchain-$version-$date-$height_xxx.tar.gz\ntar -zxvf okexchain-$version-$date-$height_xxx.tar.gz<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n<H3><s>### </s>c. 使用创世块文件，从头同步区块数据</H3>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>export EXCHAIND_PATH=~/.exchaind (或者其他目录)\nexchaind init your_custom_moniker --chain-id exchain-66 --home ${EXCHAIND_PATH}\n\nwget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okx/mainnet/main/genesis.json -O ${EXCHAIND_PATH}/config/genesis.json<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n\n\n  <br/>\n\n<H2><s>## </s>5. 启动</H2>\n<CODE lang=\"shell\"><s>```shell</s><i>\n</i>export EXCHAIN_SEEDS=\"e926c8154a2af4390de02303f0977802f15eafe2@3.16.103.80:26656,7fa5b1d1f1e48659fa750b6aec702418a0e75f13@175.41.191.69:26656,c8f32b793871b56a11d94336d9ce6472f893524b@35.74.8.189:26656\"\nexchaind start --chain-id exchain-66 --db_backend rocksdb --mempool.sort_tx_by_gp --home ${EXCHAIND_PATH} --p2p.seeds $EXCHAIN_SEEDS<i>\n</i><e>```</e></CODE>\n<p><COLOR color=\"red\"><s>[color=red]</s><br/>\n注：务必带 <C><s>`</s>--db_backend rocksdb<e>`</e></C> 参数<br/>\n<e>[/color]</e></COLOR></p>\n\n<p>你可能会出现遇到<C><s>`</s>panic: couldn\'t create db: Error initializing DB: Corruption: Unsupported compression method or corrupted compressed block contents: Snappy<e>`</e></C>这样的错误，此时需要安装<C><s>`</s>Snappy<e>`</e></C>并重新编译rocksdb，具体可以参考<URL url=\"https://github.com/facebook/rocksdb/blob/main/INSTALL.md#supported-platforms\"><s>[</s>这里<e>](https://github.com/facebook/rocksdb/blob/main/INSTALL.md#supported-platforms)</e></URL></p>\n</r>', '2021-12-21 07:34:55', 38, NULL, NULL, '43.245.196.166', 0, 1, 0, 0),
